{"tid":1241482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[低武力和理非] 向住差佬掟咩好？","createTime":"2019-06-18T17:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:13:34.000Z","uid":119173,"like":28,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1990d4f7fc5d2a6b5e071b2df5debd2990df4953","tid":1241482,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"紙飛機。<br />\n<br />\n首先要講明一樣嘢，掟紙飛機係要贏「形象」、贏民意。紙入面寫滿反佔中口號、訴求，所有想同政府講嘅說話。試諗下每排人幾十隻紙飛機飛埋班差佬，嗰個畫面幾咁震撼，足以提供素材向外間宣揚「和理非」形象。<br />\n<br />\n如果班差佬將「紙飛機」都可以講成武器，咁佢地都幾羞家。佢地一郁手撥開，就會俾人笑紙飛機都驚；唔郁手撥開就要正面食哂，同掟蛋/蕃茄一樣帶著羞辱意味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfda5cfe181733fc1f89b75fb252f37530185260","tid":1241482,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b99635f425bffa394871de9780cee72738b33d2","tid":1241482,"uid":3893,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rpo6Wrq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpo6Wrq.gif&h=3f83d36e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ee3159c407b31922bd4f38d5f74822ab6de0934","tid":1241482,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fd1b8ae363d352c250f8b6b88f34af0f15d20e","tid":1241482,"uid":119173,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"同場加映：俄羅斯群眾2018年上街抗議政府禁用Telegram<br />\n<br />\n(當然，佢地架飛機都食緊 Tg 個 icon。然而我地今次6.9, 6.12, 6.16 嘅行動其實都好大程度依靠 Telegram。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.voltron.voanews.com/Drupal/01live-166/2019-04/70A0E24D-4FA6-4D66-959A-92674FAD0EC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.voltron.voanews.com%2FDrupal%2F01live-166%2F2019-04%2F70A0E24D-4FA6-4D6